## Features

### CLI

```bash
# Fetch transcript by URL
ytt fetch "https://youtu.be/dQw4w9WgXcQ"

# Fetch by video ID
ytt fetch dQw4w9WgXcQ

# Save to file
ytt fetch dQw4w9WgXcQ -o transcript.txt

# Output as JSON
ytt fetch dQw4w9WgXcQ --json
```

